p: The panel of 186 DENV-1 viruses used in the present study was collected from symptomatic patients from 2008 to 2015 in a public healthcare facility in SJRP (São Paulo, Brazil) as part of the flavivirus and hantavirus surveillance program in the city. This study was reviewed and approved by the Human Research Ethics Committee of Faculdade de Medicina de São José do Rio Preto (CAAE: 02078812.8.00005414).
